data.description: Situated on a prime CORNER LOT, this enchanting residence showcases a covered POOL embraced by screened patio, forming a serene retreat for leisure and social gatherings. Offering 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a charming BONUS STUDIO room, the home seamlessly blends comfort with practicality. Inside, discover the sanctuary of UPGRADES, including new windows, granite countertops, and a high-end kitchen appliances. Bedrooms boast hardwood floors, adding a touch of sophistication. The property boasts a YOGA DECK, BRICK PATIO, and a recently screened pool with a NEW PUMP, reflecting the seller’s meticulous attention to detail. NEAR DISNEY, SHOPPING, 192, OLD TOWN AND MORE.
